**Capital gains tax** applies when you sell a capital asset (shares, mutual funds, property) at a profit. From FY 2024-25 onwards: LTCG on equity/equity MF is taxed at 12.5% above ₹1.25 lakh annually (no indexation), STCG on equity at 20%, and debt funds at applicable slab rates. This calculator covers all these scenarios.
